{"tid":1041932,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Biohazard 2 Remake (死唔斷氣)集中討論區 17","createTime":"2019-03-01T08:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T09:35:38.000Z","uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91684d59b757450a9254b51644e9a604b589a3f7","tid":1041932,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://t00.deviantart.net/56pvoo_Ef2Lap6Phhevs4t5pDpY=/700x350/filters:fixed_height(100,100):origin()/pre00/a3f9/th/pre/f/2018/165/f/b/resident_evil_2_remake_wallpaper_hd_by_briellalove-dceckl3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ft00.deviantart.net%2F56pvoo_Ef2Lap6Phhevs4t5pDpY%3D%2F700x350%2Ffilters%3Afixed_height%28100%2C100%29%3Aorigin%28%29%2Fpre00%2Fa3f9%2Fth%2Fpre%2Ff%2F2018%2F165%2Ff%2Fb%2Fresident_evil_2_remake_wallpaper_hd_by_briellalove-dceckl3.png&h=adc59165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇黎大家都鐘意叫BIO,就用番BIO圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意: 呢個POST有大量痴線佬,又話要人同喪屍多P交配,又話除LEON條底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Cm3ETiA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCm3ETiA.png&h=9990fd72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家生客同熟客都有得買,不過熟客可以去CAPCOM總部玩同埋會得到REMARK版遊戲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS4 , XBOX , PC (STEAM)<br />\n25/1/2019正式發售<br />\n港行係有血腥爆頭標腸版<br />\n唔想見到就自己搵日版D版<br />\n香港大致得兩種版本<br />\n(PS4為例)<br />\n普通膠盒版<br />\nCollector box (冇四條KEY,歐美版先有)<br />\n<br />\n港行冇鐵盒版<br />\n要就搵歐美版<br />\n<br />\nRemake版LEON真人Model<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/iQ7gCaUHwoToh7dgJrvacV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net%2FiQ7gCaUHwoToh7dgJrvacV.jpg&h=ad71f60e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nClaire真人Model<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/LepH62p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLepH62p.png&h=751ceaeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DhfOq5qU8AIyyVX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDhfOq5qU8AIyyVX.jpg&h=36c246e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DhfOrl7UcAAOtxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDhfOrl7UcAAOtxc.jpg&h=4380e6b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DhfOpZiVMAA39Ux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDhfOpZiVMAA39Ux.jpg&h=ead8ecff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAda Wong真人Model<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180105/photo/bkn-20180105135958215-0105_00862_001_10p.jpg?20180106051319\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180105135958215-0105_00862_001_10p.jpg%3F20180106051319&h=11600d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:點分日版同美版?<br />\nA:基本上係香港買到港行係雙封面,美版血腥版內容,再唔係可以睇隻BLURAY區碼 (1:歐美, 2:日本, 3:港行)<br />\n<br />\nQ:有冇中文字幕?<br />\nA:港行係有繁體中文字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同蝗語配音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:有冇表裏關之分?<br />\nA: 暫時睇上黎係有GE<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nby2mSw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnby2mSw.jpg&h=ef93740c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:有咩隱藏野玩?<br />\nA:官方公佈左有豆腐模式,第四生還者,GHOST模式,仲有PS1起角版男女主角用<br />\nPS1起角版LEON GAMEPLAY<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5chixBvWMeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5chixBvWMeg&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=a0d3f0b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5chixBvWMeg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四生還者HUNK GAMEPLAY (嚴重劇透,心臟有毛病或孕婦請自己決定睇唔睇)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZS87H2FmsKg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZS87H2FmsKg&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=341d62cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZS87H2FmsKg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: Mr.X點搞呀，煩過我阿媽<br />\nA: (根據巴打貓之子提供）<br />\n其實你唔跑，唔開槍，Mr. X 喺正常情況唔會跟住你<br />\n<br />\n即係一但你開完槍，再Mr. X 出場嘅音樂，就有咁快跑咁快去d 有Mr. X 頂帽嘅地方，Mr. X 唔會走入走嘅地方，你就可以慢慢觀察返Mr. X 去邊<br />\n<br />\n同理，可以用呢個方法引Mr. X 出你想去嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n另外，暫時有個場景你喺入面，Mr. X 一定會入去搵你： 洗衣房<br />\n但如果你入去係慢行，佢會喺門口望兩望就走咗去<br />\n<br />\n成就獎杯列表<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/3Tm3F4n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Tm3F4n.png&h=b0de3f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浣熊先生全位置<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ign.com/wikis/re2-remake/Mr._Raccoon_Toy_Locations\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ign.com%2Fwikis%2Fre2-remake%2FMr._Raccoon_Toy_Locations&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=ac575588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ign.com/wikis/re2-remake/Mr._Raccoon_Toy_Locations</a><br />\n由巴打讚美太陽提供<br />\n<br />\n其他精彩圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Y7dRwEz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7dRwEz.png&h=c9e6ae56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/8vnrkxV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vnrkxV.png&h=98b1de6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/mGkMkxW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGkMkxW.png&h=0e6d8765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/QvTVdSY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvTVdSY.gif&h=4ea1503b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由巴打讚美太陽提供<br />\n<br />\nPOST多次以前WESKER台果張REBECCA既相今集都有<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=25&amp;snA=53607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D25%26snA%3D53607&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=613a2204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=25&amp;snA=53607</a>"},{"pid":"9f0246eb4ac6db779f7a5e6e0eb2184ea8e1a419","tid":1041932,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:06:54.000Z","msg":"以下資料由天溢巴打提供<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.entertainment14.net/blog/post/110954657-%E6%83%A1%E9%9D%88%E5%8F%A4%E5%A0%A1-2-%E9%87%8D%E8%A3%BD%E7%89%88-%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5%E5%8C%AF%E9%9B%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.entertainment14.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F110954657-%25E6%2583%25A1%25E9%259D%2588%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25A0%25A1-2-%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E7%2589%2588-%25E6%2594%25BB%25E7%2595%25A5%25E5%258C%25AF%25E9%259B%2586&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=669148e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.entertainment14.net/blog/post/110954657-%E6%83%A1%E9%9D%88%E5%8F%A4%E5%A0%A1-2-%E9%87%8D%E8%A3%BD%E7%89%88-%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5%E5%8C%AF%E9%9B%86</a><br />\n攻略網，但建議第一次玩只睇點拎武器，享受解謎過程<br />\n<br />\nSPEED RUN<br />\nLEON A<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BMiwWOypZtM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBMiwWOypZtM&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=6ec82e8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BMiwWOypZtM</a><br />\n<br />\nCLAIRE A<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dyNl4PcZW1E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdyNl4PcZW1E&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=dd5aacab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dyNl4PcZW1E</a><br />\n]<br />\n<br />\n刀仔無傷殺G1大法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rJ5C4MnXs2I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrJ5C4MnXs2I&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=e17dad12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rJ5C4MnXs2I</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何謂表裡？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n‧一個完整故事係一個表關另一個裡關（如男表女裡/女表男裡），爆表關後可揀2ND RUN打另一角色嘅裡關<br />\n‧表裡主要分別於入警署方式唔同、道具位置唔同；裡關較早出現MR.X(舊版稱謎之敵人/暴君，所以裡關較難)、最後要打多隻G5；雖然表裡做嘅嘢大部份相同，但時間上，表關係早裡關少少。<br />\n<br />\n新舊版劇情有何分別？<br />\n‧舊版裡關有警員誤殺直升機司機導致墜機一幕，以及救火後投下謎之敵人(即MR.X，又稱暴君)一幕；表關獵食者初登場有CG。<br />\n‧舊版BOSS跟表裡，表打G幼、G2、G4，裡打G1、G3、謎之敵人正體、G5；BOSS戰分別於落下水道前、入研究所前、逃出研究所前；舊版僅裡關有謎之敵人。<br />\n‧舊版男表是ADA中槍後墜街，裡關是ADA硬食謎之敵人一拳後KISS再扮死。<br />\n‧舊版ADA是前往研究所時被G刺傷致行動不便。<br />\n‧舊版女表男裡才有SHERRY被整入胚胎劇情。<br />\n‧舊版BEN及署長是被第一次BOSS所殺。<br />\n‧舊版表關馬文畀完匙卡你後會自閉，落停車場前異變。<br />\n‧舊版沒有孤兒院，但前往孤兒院的路是舊版表關入警局前場景改成，舊玩家會感到驚喜。<br />\n‧舊版沒有植物人，是一棵移動的植物；舊版有大蜘蛛、獵食者改、大飛蛾。<br />\n‧舊版LEON武器是手槍、散彈、麥林、火槍，強化後只佔一位；CLARE為手槍、弩、榴彈(分榴彈、火炎、硫酸)；輕機槍及背包(+2)是共享給二人，即一人拿了，另一人會沒有；火箭炮是打謎之敵人正體時ADA拋下；特定條件爆機可有無限輕機槍、格靈式、火箭炮，三者皆佔兩格。<br />\n<br />\n想知更多，建議網上找gameplay<br />\n<br />\n惡靈古堡2 重製版之武器實用度評價 + 難易度感想(標準難度)<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=25&amp;snA=53500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D25%26snA%3D53500&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=fe62f10b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=25&amp;snA=53500</a><br />\n<br />\n裡關警局「頭目登場條件」＋「殭屍增援條件」實測<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=25&amp;snA=53694\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D25%26snA%3D53694&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=553c968f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=25&amp;snA=53694</a><br />\n<br />\n各武器傷害值實測<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.steamxo.com/2019/01/29/551104/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.steamxo.com%2F2019%2F01%2F29%2F551104%2F&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=d11eb024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.steamxo.com/2019/01/29/551104/</a><br />\n<br />\n由巴打神戶豆提供<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/V4umRho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4umRho.jpg&h=9d9bf216&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2184d9467f101e5cc4b2df9d25faad64734696a7","tid":1041932,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"處女POST咁就比咗BH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000848fb0153d012bcbaad3319de37a2565838c0","tid":1041932,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:30:10.000Z","msg":"繼續講打利記..不~利卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌那星...唔知邊個話4飛散搞定...或者下下近距爆頭就係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我都比隻怪下下近距爆頭呢..."},{"pid":"d7d4ee2cc0a89c2160df6818c64e92e6c54797fe","